          <div class="narm-review-title">Wonderful resource!</div>
          <div class="narm-review-meta">Peggy &nbsp;·&nbsp; <span class="narm-verified">✓ Verified Purchase</span> &nbsp;·&nbsp; December 8, 2025</div>
          <div class="narm-review-text">This book takes a very complex subject and makes the information understandable, relatable, and usable. It even provides "scripts" for counselors to address adverse childhood experiences in their clients and gives them information to help resolve complex trauma. Written with empathy and heart, it gives therapists hope in helping their clients heal.</div>
          <div class="narm-review-helpful">2 people found this helpful</div>
