          <div class="narm-review-meta">Wendy Reiersen &nbsp;·&nbsp; <span class="narm-verified">✓ Verified Purchase</span> &nbsp;·&nbsp; August 4, 2022</div>
          <div class="narm-review-text">Not only should every therapist read this book, so should every teacher, health practitioner, supervisor, and parent — anyone who interacts with people. We all have trauma. We heal through our relationships with self and others, and with generous quantities of acceptance and agency. It really is that simple. But read the book, and experience it for yourself!</div>
